        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "IRS Publication 519 描述了双重身份纳税年,适用于在同一年内对联邦税既属于 nonresident 又属于 resident 个非公民,常见于多种到达、离开搭身份调整情形,而勿仅仅跨州搬场。",
