        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "如所发证件因联邦文件而出乎意料地短期,续期辰光会影响国内航班、联邦建筑物进入,搭搬场之后可能依赖 REAL ID 个其他事项。",
