        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Illinois Secretary of State 临时访客驾照(TVDL)页面。ilsos.gov 对 curl HEAD 请求返回 302 重定向到自己页面,这是长期 .gov 域名个已知误判;该网址已通过 Secretary of State 自有索引确认。",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Illinois Student Assistance Commission 面向非美国公民学生个资源页面,包括 RISE Act 搭替代申请背景。isac.org 对非浏览器请求返回 403(反爬虫);这是已知误判。",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "移民身份 - 包括 Dreamer / DACA 身份 - 会显著影响驾照搭 REAL ID、专业执业资格(尤其是护理搭医疗)、州内学费、SSN 相关要求,搭州税申报。规则因州而异,联邦法律也常变。\n\nMoveSafe 勿能替代法律顾问。在依靠任何州对州摘要之前,请咨询持证移民律师。",
        "Immunization requirements": "免疫接种要求",
