        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "L-1 搭 O-1 专属。请按对照已批准请愿核实并咨询请愿人律师来表述。勿陈述在任何具体情形下是否要修订。勿使用 iOS SafeCopy 回避清单。",
        "Language": "语言",
        "Last verified:": "上次核实:",
        "Last verified: %@": "上次核实:%@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "合法永久居民(LPR / 绿卡持有人)碰到个州对州差异,涉及驾照证件搭 REAL ID、专业执业资格(尤其是护理 - 可能要做境外学历评估)、Medicaid 搭州医保市场资格(联邦五年等待期搭州项目相互作用)、州税申报、搭 DMV 怎么处理选民登记提示(LPR 勿能参加联邦选举,也勿能参加大多数州选举)。\n\nMoveSafe 勿能替代法律顾问。涉及身份个问题请咨询持证移民律师,跨州申报请咨询合格税务专业人士。",
