        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Massachusetts RMV 身份识别要求页面,涵盖 REAL ID、标准驾照搭合法居留文件。mass.gov 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare);这是长期 .gov 托管州门户个已知误判。",
