        "Some checklist items use placeholder sources. Replace with official sources before relying on them.": "部分清单条目使用占位来源。依靠之前请替换成官方来源。",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules.": "有些物品跨州个监管规则可能勿一样,可能涉及州法律、地方条例、联邦法律,或者机构规则。",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in any specific situation. Verify directly with official sources and consult a licensed attorney or relevant agency if needed.": "有些项目跨州个监管规则可能勿一样,可能涉及州法律、地方条例、联邦法律或机构规则。MoveSafe 勿判定任何具体情形下个持有、运输或使用个法律性质。请直接向官方来源核实,必要辰光请咨询持证律师或相关机构。",
        "Some sources have not been verified recently. Check the official website before relying on them.": "部分来源近期未核实。依靠之前请查一查官方网站。",
        "Some states issue driver licenses or state IDs to nonimmigrant visa applicants on a shortened renewal cycle that tracks the I-94 or an underlying federal document, instead of the multi-year cycle used for citizens. Fees, renewal timing, and steps after a status extension can differ between origin and destination states.": "部分州对非移民签证申请人发驾照或州身份证个续期周期较短,跟着 I-94 或者底层联邦文件,而勿是公民使用个多年周期。费用、续期辰光,搭身份延期之后个步骤,出发州搭目的州可能勿一样。",
