        "Start fresh": "重新开始",
        "Starting work at a new worksite outside the LCA's MSA without an amended petition can affect status maintenance, and the timing of the amended petition filing matters for when the worker can begin at the new location.": "在没有修订请愿个情况下,在 LCA 个 MSA 之外开始新工作地点,可能影响身份维持;修订请愿提交个辰光关系到员工啥辰光好在新地点开始工作。",
        "State DMV document checklists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 and similar) can differ from those used for U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents. Accepted combinations of passport, visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, and I-797 or employer letter may vary, and some states ask for an SSN card or an SSA ineligibility letter.": "各州 DMV 对非移民签证申请人(F-1、J-1、H-1B、L-1、O-1 等等)个证件清单可能搭美国公民或合法永久居民勿一样。可接受个护照、签证、I-94、I-20 或 DS-2019、搭 I-797 或雇主信个组合可能勿一样,部分州还要 SSN 卡或 SSA 不符合资格说明信。",
        "State University of New York Board of Trustees policy on residency for tuition purposes, including which visa categories can establish New York domicile. suny.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing state university system domain.": "State University of New York 董事会关于学费意义上居住身份个政策,包括哪些签证类别好在 New York 建立住所。suny.edu 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare);这是长期州立大学系统域名个已知误判。",
        "State filing requirements, part-year residency, remote work implications.": "州税申报要求、当年部分居住,搭远程工作影响。",
        "State grant and scholarship programs each have their own rules about whether non-citizen students may be considered, what application form (FAFSA, a state alternative, or an institutional form) is used, and what documentation is needed.": "各州助学金搭奖学金项目对非公民学生是否好被考虑,有自定个规则,使用哪种申请表(FAFSA、州替代表,或者院校自有表),要哪些文件,也都各勿相同。",
        "State labor law basics (paid sick leave, breaks, final pay rules)": "州劳动法基础(带薪病假、休息、离职结薪规则)",
        "State law": "州法律",
        "State residency basics": "州居住身份基础",
        "State tax filing can apply even when income is earned remotely. Rules differ by state.": "即便收入来自远程工作,州税申报仍可能适用。各州个规则不一样。",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. A person treated as a nonresident alien on the federal return may still be a resident, part-year resident, or nonresident for state purposes depending on domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors. States may or may not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "州税居住身份按各州自己个规则认定,可能搭联邦税务居住身份勿一样。在联邦申报上被视为 nonresident alien 个人,在州一级根据住所、实际居留日数、雇主地点搭其他因素,仍可能是居民、当年部分居住,或者非居民。各州对联邦税务条约豁免可能采纳、也可能勿采纳。",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. Domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors can each play a role.": "州税居住身份按各州自己个规则认定,可能搭联邦税务居住身份勿一样。住所、实际居留日数、雇主地点搭其他因素,都可能各自起作用。",
        "State tax withholding, labor law basics, remote work considerations.": "州税预扣、劳动法基础,搭远程工作考量。",
        "States and individual public colleges and universities use different tuition-classification rules for non-citizens, including how prior in-state high school attendance, current immigration status, and a parent's residency are considered.": "各州搭各公立大专院校对非公民个学费分类规则勿一样,包括之前在本州就读高中、当前移民身份,搭父母居住情况是怎么考虑个。",
        "States may require proof of identity, residency, lawful presence, school documents, or other paperwork.": "各州可能要身份证明、居住证明、合法居留证明、学校文件,或者其他材料。",
