        "USCIS Policy Manual chapter that describes federal address-change reporting.": "USCIS 政策手册中描述联邦地址变更报告个章节。",
        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "USCIS 存档页面,总结 2015 Simeio Solutions 最终指引,搭工作地点变更出 MSA 触发 LCA 修订个情形。",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "USCIS 指引一般表明 USPS 地址变更勿会更改 USCIS 个记录,USPS 也勿转寄 USCIS 个邮件。目的州 DMV 地址更新搭联邦 AR-11 申报也是分开个两个步骤。",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "USCIS 指引一般表明,H-1B 员工换到现有 LCA 同一 MSA 或拟雇用地区之内个新工作地点,勿要新 LCA 或修订 H-1B 请愿,但现有 LCA 可能仍要在新工作地点张贴。员工仍要遵守联邦 AR-11 地址变更要求。",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "USCIS 新闻室通告,介绍在线地址变更工具,并阐明 USPS 转寄勿会更改 USCIS 记录。",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "USCIS 关于联邦地址变更要求个总览页,包括在线地址变更工具。",
        "USPS Mail Forwarding / Change of Address": "USPS 邮件转寄 / 地址变更",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "USPS 邮件转寄页面;引用是为了阐明,按 USCIS 指引,USPS 地址变更勿能代替联邦 AR-11 申报。",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "按 22 CFR Part 62,J-1 项目主办方维护 SEVIS 记录并监督每位交流访问学者个活动地点。搬场改变了住所、活动地点或者接待机构辰光,一般触发交流访问学者向主办方个报告义务,搭主办方对 SEVIS 个更新。",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "根据 USCIS 在 Matter of Simeio Solutions(2015)之后个指引,H-1B 员工换到当前 LCA 上所列 MSA 或拟雇用地区之外个工作地点,一般属重大变更,要新个 LCA 搭修订过个 H-1B 请愿。",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "了解目的州对居住身份个定义",
        "Undocumented Student Liaisons - Illinois Board of Higher Education": "无身份学生联络人 - Illinois Board of Higher Education",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "University of California 招生页面,介绍 AB 540 非居民学费豁免,并指出大多数非移民签证持有人(比如 F-1 或 J-1)一般勿能在 California 建立学费意义上个居住身份。",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "更新雇佣文件搭州税表",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "请使用「勿好假设」类措辞。勿陈述 USPS 或 DMV 更新可替代 AR-11(USCIS 指引一般表明勿能替代)。勿使用 iOS SafeCopy 回避清单(法律结论搭规避处罚个措辞)。",
